{"tid":271891,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！i9正式發佈 2000美元癲價開賣","createTime":"2017-06-05T12:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T06:08:10.000Z","uid":2515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"430b5906b57d23c44440a3292d3164a2ca4a7732","tid":271891,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:14:34.000Z","msg":"去年的 Computex 上，Intel 發表了首款的消費級十核心 Core i7 處理器，當時 1,700 多美元的定價就已經把我們嚇得不輕，十核似乎又也有點過頭了。不過一年過去了，隨著 AMD 的 16 核心處理器發表，桌機高核心數之戰的序幕已然開啟，Intel 也該拿出點什麼來回應 AMD 咄咄逼人的挑戰。原先預期會是最高 12 核心的 Core i9 處理器，這下子最高階款被一口氣推到了 18 核心 / 36 執行緒之多，確保在紙面上的規格保持絶對的壓制，同時 Intel 將 X 系列擴展成了獨立的 Core i9 系列，並預計首批將一共推出四款新品。"},{"pid":"04ed9909f8539f033ac9ccf6fe2d7ece03755a6c","tid":271891,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:19:32.000Z","msg":"會幾熱？"},{"pid":"6aea1abb43c4b8669e136e5e31343d9339e7061f","tid":271891,"uid":376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"手機台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221ce828cfd566c69518a3a2a02a8d69a4250db5","tid":271891,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:34:13.000Z","msg":"2000美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4417a0cd5801e01aea698d9990d9c7e0f189636","tid":271891,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:35:12.000Z","msg":"突乜野發，成個星期前"},{"pid":"b58a395ec0bcd4f33bfc60b71e4ea567bc8d2ddd","tid":271891,"uid":104613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:36:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3265f69e1c13e9fcedb279f8dfda989d15925f3b","tid":271891,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2000美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實二千蚊美金唔算貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />